---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Nossos Institutos"
    description="Conheça os Institutos do Grupo Espírita Paulo de Tarso (GEPT): Criança, Jovem, Esclarecimento e Família, Mediunidade, Caridade e Divulgação."
>
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Nossos Institutos</h1>
                <p class="text-brand-muted max-w-xl mx-auto text-lg">Nossas atividades estão organizadas em departamentos especializados para melhor atender e apoiar a comunidade através da doutrina espírita.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 hover-card group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-brand-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Instituto da Caridade</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Coordena a assistência social, oferecendo auxílio a famílias em situação de vulnerabilidade, distribuição de alimentos e liderando nossas campanhas fraternas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 hover-card group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-brand-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Instituto da Criança</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Gerencia a Evangelização Infantil, focando no desenvolvimento e educação moral cristã para nossas crianças.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 hover-card group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-brand-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Instituto do Jovem</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Gerencia a Mocidade Espírita, proporcionando espaço e acolhimento para o desenvolvimento moral e social da juventude.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 hover-card group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-brand-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Instituto do Esclarecimento e Família</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Responsável pela orientação familiar e pelos ciclos de estudos aprofundados da Doutrina Espírita.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 hover-card group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-brand-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Instituto da Divulgação</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Responsável pela biblioteca espírita, livraria, difusão da doutrina e comunicação institucional nas mídias digitais.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 hover-card group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-brand-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Instituto da Mediunidade</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Conduz a Escola de Médiuns e coordena com responsabilidade o amparo mediúnico nas salas de tratamento espiritual e reuniões específicas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
